  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      this study is an individual patient level meta-analysis of randomized clinical trials, to
      evaluate the influence of ethnicity, to study whether the relative tradeoff between ischemia
      and bleeding is distinct by ethnicity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
